            <li class="bad-item"><span class="x-icon">✕</span><span>Expensive to replace when dropped</span></li>
            <li class="bad-item"><span class="x-icon">✕</span><span>Battery dies when they're scrolling</span></li>
            <li class="bad-item"><span class="x-icon">✕</span><span>Distracted — won't answer when you call</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="compare-vs">
          <div class="vs-circle">VS</div>
        </div>

        <div class="compare-card compare-good">
          <div class="compare-card-badge">Recommended</div>
          <div class="compare-card-header">
            <div class="compare-icon-wrap good"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#46c160" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle><path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20"></path><path d="M2 12h20"></path></svg></div>
            <div>
              <div class="compare-card-title">Tracki Universal</div>
              <div class="compare-card-sub">Just $14.90 — world's smallest GPS</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="compare-list">
            <li class="good-item"><span class="check-icon">✓</span><span>Screen-free — zero distraction, infinite focus</span></li>
            <li class="good-item"><span class="check-icon">✓</span><span>No internet access · No apps · No stranger danger</span></li>
            <li class="good-item"><span class="check-icon">✓</span><span>Tiny, lightweight, nearly indestructible</span></li>
            <li class="good-item"><span class="check-icon">✓</span><span>7-day battery · gets an alert before it dies</span></li>
            <li class="good-item"><span class="check-icon">✓</span><span>One button tap sends you an instant text</span></li>
          </ul>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-green btn-pill newparents-buy-btn" onclick="buyTrackiUniversalCheckout(this)">Get Tracki Now →</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Action Button Highlight -->
      <div class="action-highlight">
        <div class="action-highlight-icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#46c160" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div class="action-highlight-text">
          <h3>The Programmable Action Button — Your Child's Secret Superpower</h3>
