            </div>
            <div class="feature-card-tag">Instant Alert</div>
            <h3>3-Second SOS Panic Button</h3>
            <p>Hold 3 seconds → your phone rings immediately with exact GPS coordinates. Stranger danger, fall, or feeling unsafe — help is one squeeze away.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Wi-Fi Indoor -->
        <div class="feature-card" data-delay="100">
          <div class="feature-card-bg" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d1f3c,#0a3d62)"></div>
          <div class="feature-card-overlay" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(13,31,60,.6),rgba(10,61,98,.4))"></div>
          <div class="feature-card-content">
            <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12.55a11 11 0 0 1 14.08 0"/><path d="M1.42 9a16 16 0 0 1 21.16 0"/><path d="M8.53 16.11a6 6 0 0 1 6.95 0"/><circle cx="12" cy="20" r="1" fill="#fff"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card-tag">Works Everywhere</div>
            <h3>Wi-Fi Indoor Tracking</h3>
            <p>Standard GPS goes dark inside buildings. Tracki uses nearby Wi-Fi signals to pinpoint them deep inside malls, theme parks, schools, and stadiums.</p>
            <div class="feature-chip-row">
              <span class="chip chip-dark">Schools</span>
              <span class="chip chip-dark">Stadiums</span>
              <span class="chip chip-dark">Malls</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Geofencing -->
