            </div>
            <div class="feature-card-tag">Smart Notifications</div>
            <h3>Geofencing &amp; Smart 'Places'</h3>
            <p>Draw a virtual boundary around school, grandma's, or the park. When they arrive or leave — you get an instant text: <em>"Anna arrived at School ✓"</em> — not confusing coordinates.</p>
            <div class="geofence-demo">
              <div class="geofence-circle"><div class="geofence-pin-svg"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#46c160"><path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7zm0 9.5c-1.38 0-2.5-1.12-2.5-2.5s1.12-2.5 2.5-2.5 2.5 1.12 2.5 2.5-1.12 2.5-2.5 2.5z"/></svg></div></div>
              <div class="geofence-label">School Geofence Active</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4: Route History -->
        <div class="feature-card" data-delay="300">
          <div class="feature-card-bg" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a2e,#2d2d5e)"></div>
          <div class="feature-card-overlay" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(26,26,46,.5),rgba(45,45,94,.3))"></div>
          <div class="feature-card-content">
            <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card-tag">Route History</div>
            <h3>Live Breadcrumbs &amp; Trip Replay</h3>
            <p>Review the exact route they walked, step by step. Confirm they didn't take that unsafe shortcut — and verify their walk matched what they told you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 5: Ultra-Lightweight -->
        <div class="feature-card" data-delay="400">
          <div class="feature-card-bg" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1a0a3a,#2d1a5e)"></div>
          <div class="feature-card-content">
            <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card-tag">1.26 oz Only</div>
            <h3>Ultra-Lightweight &amp; Wearable</h3>
            <p>Lighter than a granola bar. Kids forget they're wearing it. Includes lanyard, belt clip, and backpack velcro — perfect for any child, any day.</p>
            <div class="weight-badge">
              <span class="weight-num">1.26</span>
              <span class="weight-unit">oz</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 6: Battery Alerts -->
        <div class="feature-card" data-delay="500">
          <div class="feature-card-bg" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1c1200,#3d2800)"></div>
          <div class="feature-card-overlay" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(28,18,0,.5),rgba(61,40,0,.3))"></div>
          <div class="feature-card-content">
            <div class="feature-icon-wrap">
              <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card-tag">Never Goes Missing</div>
            <h3>App Beeper &amp; Battery Alerts</h3>
            <p>Dropped it in the grass? Ring it remotely from the app. Get an automatic notification when battery hits 10% — never dead in an emergency.</p>
            <div class="battery-bar-wrap">
              <div class="battery-bar"><div class="battery-fill" style="width:87%"></div></div>
